OL,12,FJanuary 2023 after an Ofsted report
OL,13,Fdowngraded Caversham Primary School
OL,14,Ffrom its highest rating,
OL,15,F"outstanding", to its lowest rating,
OL,16,F"inadequate", over safeguarding
OL,17,Fconcerns.
