OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV Meridian, Julia Waters
OL,7,Fsaid "The review hasn't looked
OL,8,Fconsistently and rigorously enough at
OL,9,Fthe questions it was meant to be
OL,10,Flooking at.
OL,12,F"Namely, what actions did Reading
OL,13,FBorough Council take, and what actions
OL,14,Fcould or should it have taken to
OL,15,Fsupport Ruth better and that might
OL,16,Fhave prevented her death."
OL,18,FThe Coroner at the inquest into Ms
OL,19,FPerry's death recorded a narrative
OL,20,Fconclusion of suicide, contributed to
OL,21,Fby an Ofsted inspection.
