OL,6,FReading Borough Council said it has
OL,7,Falready taken steps to better
OL,8,Funderstand and respond to the
OL,9,Fpressures on headteachers and the
OL,10,Fimpact on their wellbeing.
OL,12,FJackie Yates, Reading Borough Council
OL,13,FChief Executive, said: "We are
OL,14,Fenormously grateful to everybody
OL,15,Finvolved for their input into the
OL,16,FIndependent Learning Review, including
OL,17,FRuth's family, and the headteachers
OL,18,Fand Governors from across our school
OL,19,Fcommunity, including Caversham Primary.
