OL,4,Clife says review a 'missed opportunity'
OL,6,F"While acknowledging the proactive
OL,7,Fapproach taken by Reading in
OL,8,Fsupporting schools before, during and
OL,9,Fafter Ofsted inspections, including at
OL,10,FCaversham Primary, the report also
OL,11,Fhighlights a number of areas for
OL,12,Ffurther improvement which we fully
OL,13,Facknowledge and which we intend to
OL,14,Fmeasure progress against through an
OL,15,Fassociated action plan.
OL,17,F"This will build upon the list of
OL,18,Fsteps already taken to support local
OL,19,Fschools.
