OL,4,Clife says review a 'missed opportunity'
OL,6,F"The Independent Learning Review
OL,7,Frecognises that Reading finds itself
OL,8,Fin a unique position, through the most
OL,9,Ftragic circumstances, to make powerful
OL,10,Frepresentations to Ofsted, which we
OL,11,Fhave done as part of the Big Listen
OL,12,Fconsultation.
OL,14,F"It is our strong belief that the
OL,15,Fdiscussion should ultimately lead to
OL,16,Fpositive changes which support our
OL,17,Fheadteachers and which debunk the myth
OL,18,Fthat the current approach provides
OL,19,Fimprovements in the quality of
OL,20,Feducation for our children."
