OL,6,FMs Perry's death also led to concerns
OL,7,Fover the way Ofsted uses single-phrase
OL,8,Fratings.
OL,10,FBut despite calls for them to be
OL,11,Fscrapped, the Government at the time
OL,12,Finsisted it remains committed to
OL,13,Fsingle-phrase Ofsted judgments
OL,15,FThe Department for Education (DfE) has
OL,16,Fsaid it would "continue to listen to
OL,17,Fviews and look at alternative
OL,18,Fsystems", but it believes there are
OL,19,F"significant benefits" to headline
OL,20,Fgrades awarded in England by the
OL,21,Fschools watchdog.
