OL,6,FJust a few months ago a survey
OL,7,Frevealed more than four out of five
OL,8,Fteachers in England believe a new
OL,9,Fsystem of inspection should be
OL,10,Fintroduced because Ofsted has "many
OL,11,Fproblems".
OL,13,FThe majority of teachers asked (90%)
OL,14,Fsaid they do not believe single-word
OL,15,Fjudgments are a fair reflection of the
OL,16,Fperformance of a school.
