OL,6,FA poll, of more than 4,500 National
OL,7,FEducation Union (NEU) teacher members
OL,8,Fin state schools in England, suggests
OL,9,F62% feel the inspection system causes
OL,10,Fthem mental ill-health and 59% say it
OL,11,Faffects their home life.
OL,13,FResponding to today's report an Ofsted
OL,14,Fspokesperson said: "Ruth Perry's death
OL,15,Fwas a tragedy and we are determined to
OL,16,Fdo everything in our power to prevent
OL,17,Fsuch tragedies in the future.
OL,19,F"That's why we accepted the HM
OL,20,FCoroner's report in full and responded
OL,21,Fto each of its recommendations.
