OL,6,F"As part of this, we carried out a Big
OL,7,FListen consultation to help us build
OL,8,Fan Ofsted that is trusted by the
OL,9,Fprofessionals we inspect and regulate,
OL,10,Fas well as the children, learners,
OL,11,Fparents and carers we are here to
OL,12,Fserve.
OL,14,F"And we commissioned an independent
OL,15,Flearning review of our response to
OL,16,FRuth's death, led by Dame Christine
OL,17,FGilbert.
OL,19,F"We will report back on the findings
OL,20,Fof both the Big Listen and the
OL,21,Flearning review in the autumn."
